    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Features above sea level that are man-made rather than natural. Included are large mounds and other features that resemble natural features; excluded are buildings and bridges.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
